metadata.name: Giddy Gimples #1
metadata.description: Giddy Gimples: The Chubby Edition is a collection of NFTs featuring a cast of lovable, chubby aliens who have traveled from far-off planets to bring laughter and joy to the universe. These rotund extraterrestrial characters come in all shapes and sizes, each with their own unique personalities and quirks. From a group of clumsy alien foodies on a mission to try every weird and wacky dish in the galaxy to a trio of mischievous alien pranksters who always seem to get themselves into sticky situations, the Giddy Gimples are guaranteed to bring a smile to your face. Collect all of the Giddy Gimples and let their zany antics and loveable jigginess brighten up your digital world.
